    {
      "title": "[负面] CAN'T EVEN GET IT TO RUN.  Hangs while loading ini...",
      "summary": "CAN'T EVEN GET IT TO RUN.  Hangs while loading initial data.  Have to force quit and restart to fix.  Then click the \"Enter Mythag\" button at the bottom, and it hangs on the login.  Have to force quit and restart to fix.  Then have to click \"Enter Mythag\" a second time to actually enter the game, and it hangs trying to start the game.  Unfortunately, this is NOT fixed with a force quit and restart.  Whenever I used the \"Fix\" feature, that just simply restarted the whole hanging sequence all over, again.\n\nSo, I'm literally UNABLE to play the game.  And it's a shame, because I was really interested in this game for the artwork.  However, if the game is so poorly coded that it is just unable to run, that's not a frustration I'm willing to fight through.",
      "source": "steam_review",
